<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>After updating from ZendFramework Version 1.6 to 1.6.1 this message occours.</p>

<pre class="highlight"><code>
Notice: No translation for the language 'de_DE' available. in...
</code></pre>

<p>Reproducable only if I manually set the locale</p>

<pre class="highlight"><code>
$translate-&gt;setLocale(Zend_Registry::get(J3k_Registry::LOCALE)-&gt;toString());
</code></pre>

<p>Affects the gettext Adapter!</p>

<p>Just forget to say that the right language files are used and translated! It's just the message...</p>

